com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium

Class ContextMenu

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.ContextMenu

  • public final class ContextMenu
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides access to context menu items and allows notifying Chromium engine about context menu state.
    提供对上下文菜单项的访问，并允许将上下文菜单状态通知给Chromium引擎。

      • notifyItemSelected

        public void notifyItemSelected(ContextMenuItem item)
        Notifies Chromium engine that the given context menu item has been selected. Chromium will execute corresponding functionality of the selected context menu item.
        通知Chromium引擎已选择给定的上下文菜单项。 Chromium将执行所选上下文菜单项的相应功能。
        Parameters:
        item - selected context menu item. Cannot be null. -选定的上下文菜单项。不可能是 。
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - when item is null.

      • notifyContextMenuOpened

        public void notifyContextMenuOpened()
        Notifies Chromium engine that context menu has been opened. Can be invoked multiple times.
        通知Chromium引擎上下文菜单已打开。可以多次调用。

      • notifyContextMenuClosed

        public void notifyContextMenuClosed()
        Notifies Chromium engine that context menu has been closed. Can be invoked multiple times. Chromium engine will update context menu state flag. When context menu is closed, Chromium ignores notifyItemSelected(ContextMenuItem) calls.
        通知Chromium引擎上下文菜单已关闭。可以多次调用。 Chromium引擎将更新上下文菜单状态标志。关闭上下文菜单后，Chromium会忽略notifyItemSelected（ContextMenuItem）调用。
